OL,7,FHe was looking forward to being
OL,8,Freunited with "literally dozens" of
OL,9,Ffriends, after a carefree year of
OL,10,Ftravelling in South America.
OL,12,FBut ten of Nehoray's close friends
OL,13,Fnever made it home from the desert.
OL,15,FThey were among more than 350 people
OL,16,Fwho that lost their lives when Hamas
OL,17,Fgunmen swarmed the Nova trance
OL,18,Ffestival site at sunrise on October 7,
OL,19,F2023.
