OL,7,F"Before October 7 everything was
OL,8,Fhappiness and fun for me and I was
OL,9,Fjust starting my life as someone's who
OL,10,Fis only 24," Nehoray told ITV News.
OL,12,F"I had a whole plan for my grown up-
OL,13,Flife, but everything shifted. My point
OL,14,Fof view, my mindset, my way of
OL,15,Fthinking - everything changed,
OL,16,Feverything."
