OL,7,FOf the estimated 4,000 people who
OL,8,Fattended Nova, the majority were in
OL,9,Ftheir late teens or early twenties -
OL,10,Fthe same age as Nehoray and his
OL,11,Ffriends.
OL,13,FIt's an age when going to trance
OL,14,Ffestival is almost a rite of passage
OL,15,Fin Israel, often following military
OL,16,Fservice and a year abroad.
OL,18,FLike so many who survived the
OL,19,Findiscriminate shooting and terror
OL,20,Fthat day, Nehoray's harrowing account
OL,21,Fgoes from utter bliss to sheer terror.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
