OL,7,FWhen the sirens first went off, he
OL,8,Fshrugged it off as a regular
OL,9,Foccurrence in Israel and sent a casual
OL,10,Fselfie to his parents to reassure them
OL,11,Feverything was "cool".
OL,13,FBut within hours he was recording a
OL,14,Ffarewell message to his family,
OL,15,Fconvinced that he would not make it
OL,16,Fout alive.
