OL,10,FAs it became clear that the festival
OL,11,Fwas under attack, Nehoray said he
OL,12,Fstarted to run, but turned back to
OL,13,Fhelp others get to safety.
OL,15,FSome were frozen with terror; others
OL,16,Fwere struggling to accept it was real
OL,17,Fbecause they were drunk or had taken
OL,18,Fpsychedelic drugs.
