OL,7,F"It was hard because the atmosphere
OL,8,Fwas that you're with your friends,
OL,9,Fdancing in the rain, you're not
OL,10,Fthinking about being hunted down by
OL,11,Fthousands of terrorists," Nehoray said.
OL,13,F"We needed to actually convince them
OL,14,Fthat something real is going on,
OL,15,Fbecause they thought we were
OL,16,Fhallucinating or something."
