OL,7,FWhen he finally fled for safety,
OL,8,FNehoray witnessed what he calls "an
OL,9,Fapocalypse". Two people were shot
OL,10,Fright next to him as he was running
OL,11,Ffor cover.
OL,13,F"Those were the moments when you're
OL,14,Freally feeling overwhelming
OL,15,Fhelplessness," he recalled.
OL,17,F"Because you're running for your life,
OL,18,Fbut at the same time, you're getting
OL,19,Fpeople dying and screaming for help.
OL,20,FAnd you know you can't do anything;
OL,21,Fyou can't go back."
