OL,7,FThe final death toll was 364,
OL,8,Faccording to police. In addition, 40
OL,9,Ffestival goers were taken hostage by
OL,10,FHamas. It was one of the worst
OL,11,Fcivilian atrocities in Israel's
OL,12,Fhistory.
OL,14,FAlthough thousands escaped with their
OL,15,Flives and their liberty, some were
OL,16,Fbadly wounded, others were raped or
OL,17,Fsexually assaulted, and many have told
OL,18,Fof being eyewitness to scenes of
OL,19,Funimaginable horror.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
