OL,7,F"The question that was in my head all
OL,8,Fthe time was, why did I survive?,"
OL,9,Fsaid Nehoray, who is now being treated
OL,10,Ffor post-traumatic stress disorder
OL,11,F(PTSD).
OL,13,F"We lost a lot of people that day. So
OL,14,Fwhy me?"
OL,16,FIt's a common question, according to
OL,17,FSafe Heart, a non-profit organisation
OL,18,Fwhich provides clinical therapy and
OL,19,Fretreats for Nova festival survivors.
