OL,7,FSafe Heart, which was set up in the
OL,8,Fimmediate aftermath of the massacre,
OL,9,Fis now supporting 1,300 people.
OL,11,FCo-founder Yair Grynbaum told ITV News
OL,12,Fthat, as Israelis deal with the
OL,13,Fcollective trauma of the conflicts
OL,14,Fthat have followed October 7, more and
OL,15,Fmore people need a diminishing number
OL,16,Fof resources.
OL,18,FOne year is not long enough to recover
OL,19,Ffrom such an ordeal and festival
OL,20,Fsurvivors require long term support,
OL,21,Faccording to Grynbaum.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
