OL,7,F"Many don't have the means or the
OL,8,Fsocial or mental ability to take care
OL,9,Fof themselves," he said. "As time
OL,10,Fprogresses, it just becomes more
OL,11,Fdifficult."
OL,13,FHe said Safe Heart is helping
OL,14,Fsurvivors with complex issues, from
OL,15,Fdeep depression and psychosis to
OL,16,Faddiction. Some have returned to work
OL,17,Fdespite not being fit to do so, while
OL,18,Fothers are unable to feed or wash
OL,19,Fthemselves without their family's
OL,20,Fsupport.
