OL,5,Cyear on
OL,7,FAnd the anniversary has proved to be
OL,8,Fan emotional trigger. In the days
OL,9,Fleading up to it, Safe Heart saw a
OL,10,Fsignificant rise in patients failing
OL,11,Fto make therapy appointments or having
OL,12,Fdifficulty sleeping.
OL,14,F"There are flashbacks, so there's a
OL,15,Fregression right now, because the
OL,16,Fstress is immense," Grynbaum said.
OL,17,F"And it's not only the one year
OL,18,Fanniversary, Israel is bleeding all
OL,19,Fover."
