OL,7,F"Think how weird it is that you have
OL,8,Fbeen to a festival with your friends,
OL,9,Fyou are enjoying the climax of the
OL,10,Fevening, enjoying your best time of
OL,11,Flife, seeing the sunrise, and then the
OL,12,Frockets come and people are fleeing
OL,13,Fall around and then terrorists are
OL,14,Fentering the party and you are running
OL,15,Ffor your life," he explained. "And
OL,16,Fyour friends are falling beside you.
OL,18,F"There's a big issue with survivor
OL,19,Fblame. A lot of them say 'that bullet
OL,20,Fwas aimed at me, but he died'.
