OL,7,F"They feel that if I have survived
OL,8,Fthis, there must be the reason, and
OL,9,Fthe reason is that I will keep their
OL,10,Fstories alive."
OL,12,FThat was echoed by Nehoray.
OL,14,F"I survived for a reason," he said. "I
OL,15,Fdecided I'm going to live my life for
OL,16,Fme, and for my ten friends who that I
OL,17,Flost.
