OL,7,F"I am trying to take advantage of
OL,8,Fevery minute that I am alive and am
OL,9,Fable to do something, because
OL,10,Fsometimes I am not able, because of
OL,11,Fthe flashbacks, the triggers, the
OL,12,Fintensity of feelings and emotions."
OL,14,FNehoray is now following his childhood
OL,15,Fdream of becoming an actor and has
OL,16,Fjust completed his first year of
OL,17,Facting school.
