OL,7,FHowever, he opted to mark the
OL,8,Fanniversary of his friends' deaths by
OL,9,Fspeaking about his experience at an
OL,10,Fawareness raising event in the US.
OL,12,FAnd he is now encouraging other
OL,13,Fsurvivors to seek therapy and to speak
OL,14,Fabout their ordeal.
OL,16,FHe wants them to accept there will be
OL,17,Ftough days but urges them "to choose
OL,18,Flife".
